{"id":6105,"date":"2014-12-22T11:30:31","date_gmt":"2014-12-22T10:30:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/?p=6105"},"modified":"2014-12-22T12:16:45","modified_gmt":"2014-12-22T11:16:45","slug":"festival-crew-and-artist-catering-for-shangri-la-at-glastonbury","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/festival-crew-and-artist-catering-for-shangri-la-at-glastonbury\/","title":{"rendered":"Festival Crew and Artist Catering for Shangri-La at Glastonbury"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Some would say that there are possibly easier places to cut your festival catering \u2018teeth\u2019 than Glastonbury\u2019s infamous <strong>Shangri-La<\/strong>. In fact, no caterer has ever returned and many have literally sunk head-first into the infamous Somerset mud along the way. Robin Collings from Shangri-La first contacted us back in 2012 and explained how he had heard good things about Red Radish from the guys at <a title=\"Block9 Website\" href=\"http:\/\/www.block9.com\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Block9<\/strong><\/a> who we had catered for on a couple of events on-off festivals. Robin explained how they were looking for crew and artist catering over a month long period. Numbers would be around <strong>500 per service<\/strong> and they wanted a good Full-English breakfast option followed by some great lunch and dinner choices. Queues had to be kept to a minimum and the food needed to be hearty and substantial as their production team worked incredibly hard, especially during the build and the break.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/DSC00686.jpg\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[6105]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6117\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/DSC00686.jpg\" alt=\"Glastonbury Crew Catering\" width=\"640\" height=\"595\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/DSC00686.jpg 640w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/DSC00686-600x558.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/DSC00686-300x278.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/DSC00686-332x309.jpg 332w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Red Radish<\/strong> needed to supply a complete field-kitchen including everything from the ovens through to the knives and forks and even the kitchen-sink(s)! They were obviously worried after the problems they had suffered with catering companies in the past, but our organised approach and excellent references gave them the confidence to award us the gig for 2013 and guess what?&#8230;&#8230;.. We went back in 2014 as well. In <a title=\"Debs Armstrong Reference\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/?p=6123&amp;preview=true\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Debs Armstrong\u2019s <\/strong><\/a>very own words Red Radish were the first crew catering company <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">EVER<\/span> to not break on site!<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-22-at-11.04.10.png\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[6105]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6107\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-22-at-11.04.10.png\" alt=\"Shangri-La\" width=\"868\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-22-at-11.04.10.png 868w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-22-at-11.04.10-600x231.png 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-22-at-11.04.10-300x115.png 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/12\/Screen-Shot-2014-12-22-at-11.04.10-436x167.png 436w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 868px) 100vw, 868px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Some would say that there are possibly easier places to cut your festival catering \u2018teeth\u2019 than Glastonbury\u2019s infamous Shangri-La. In fact, no caterer has ever returned and many have literally&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/festival-crew-and-artist-catering-for-shangri-la-at-glastonbury\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6111,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[27,11],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6105","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-festivals","category-latest-blog-postings"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Festival Crew and Artist Catering for Shangri-La at Glastonbury - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/festival-crew-and-artist-catering-for-shangri-la-at-glastonbury\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Festival Crew and Artist Catering for Shangri-La at Glastonbury - Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Some would say that there are possibly easier places to cut your festival catering \u2018teeth\u2019 than Glastonbury\u2019s infamous Shangri-La. In fact, no caterer has ever returned and many 